A simple, high-efficiency, and real-time video server
Your Personal Streaming Service for music

overview.overview: Navidrome 可以用作独立服务器，允许您使用 Web 浏览器浏览和收听您的音乐收藏。

childMarkdownRemark.html:
• Handles very large music collections
  • Streams virtually any audio format available
  • Reads and uses all your beautifully curated metadata
  • Great support for compilations (Various Artists albums) and box sets (multi-disc albums)
  • Multi-user, each user has their own play counts, playlists, favorites, etc..
